column2: SELECT top #    p.ra AS sdss_p_ra, p.dec AS sdss_p_dec,    s.specObjId as sdss_s_specObjId, s.plate, s.fiberID, s.mjd, s.ra as sdss_s_ra, s.dec as sdss_s_dec, s.z as sdss_s_z, s.zerr as sdss_s_zerr, s.zwarning as sdss_s_zwarning, s.class as sdss_s_class, s.subClass as sdss_s_subClass,    dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as sdss_p_type, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z,    e.Flux_OIII_#, e.Flux_OIII_#_Err, e.Flux_Cont_OIII_#, e.Flux_Cont_OIII_#_Err, e.Flux_OIII_#, e.Flux_OIII_#_Err, e.Flux_Cont_OIII_#, e.Flux_Cont_OIII_#_Err,    e.Flux_Hb_#, e.Flux_Hb_#_Err, e.Flux_Cont_Hb_#, e.Flux_Cont_Hb_#_Err, e.Flux_NII_#, e.Flux_NII_#_Err, e.Flux_Cont_NII_#, e.Flux_Cont_NII_#_Err,    e.Flux_Ha_#, e.Flux_Ha_#_Err, e.Flux_Cont_Ha_#, e.Flux_Cont_Ha_#_Err into mydb.MyTable from SpecObjAll as s    LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON p.objID = s.bestObjID    LEFT JOIN emissionLinesPort as e on s.specObjID = e.specObjID    where s.z<# and s.class=&&& and s.subClass=&&&    ORDER by sdss_p_ra
